 wants to take that digital vision a step further the amount of growth weve been able to create organically is something that we would now like to open to client business in the advertising arena says ms gottesman adding that cablevision systems corp wants to develop an identity as a marketer distributor and retailer of products one idea being discussed is to sell newspaper and magazine subscriptions or even highdefinition tv sets through the cable operators digital platform emphasizing her digital mission earlier this year ms gottesman moved to exec vpdigital marketing and commerce reporting directly to chief operating officer tom rutledge patricia has been the architect of cablevisions extremely successful presentation of its products to consumers she was instrumental in creating the interactive optimum suite of advanced video products says char beales presidentceo of the cable  telecommunications association for marketing in this article special report women to watch  most popular become a member register now renew membership benefits datacenter site by area  patricia a gottesman executive profile  biography  bloomberg july    pm et media company overview of world wrestling entertainment inc snapshotpeople  overviewboard memberscommittees executive profile patricia a gottesman independent director world wrestling entertainment incagetotal calculated compensationthis person is connected to  board members in  different organizations across  different industriessee board relationships background ms patricia a gottesman was founder and principal for omnibus pg ms gottesman serves as the chairman of the advisory board of ninah the global management and analytics consulting unit of the parisbased publicis groupe ms gottesman serves in advisory roles for techmahindra ms gottesman is a csuite executive with expertise in digital media analytics marketing operations and new product development ms gottesman served as the chief executive officer and president  of crimson hexagon inc from  to  prior to crimson hexagon she held top pl roles in product marketing and brand strategy business and operations at cablevision systems corporation she served as an executive vice president of product management of cablevision systems corporation since january  and also served as its executive vice president of marketing digital marketing  commerce she was responsible for marketing all of cablevisions telecommunications products she led cablevision systems corp nyse cvc new digital marketing  commerce group ms gottesman served as senior product development and marketing executive of cablevision systems corp for more than a decade she served with cablevision for  years and served as its senior vice president of marketing she served as senior vice president of development at cablevision systems corporation she served as a director of rentrak corporation since august   she has been a director of crimson hexagon inc since december  she has been an independent director at world wrestling entertainment inc since june  she serves on the board of directors of wwe she has been a member of board of advisors at razorsight corporation since march   she serves as a member of the board of advisors at elucido media networks pvt ltd she served as a director at comscore inc since december   ms gottesman serves in advisory roles for america india foundation she is a trustee for the washingtonbased committee for economic development ced she received the ncta vanguard award shared responsibility with the operating team for delivering a  billion annual consumer and smb revenue budget led the member branding marketing and product teams that developed and executed the cable industry’s optimum branding and triple play acquisition strategy was one of three inventors on an adtech cable patent and led the brand and product teams that won two natas emmy awards for digital interactive television ms gottesman graduated magna cum laude from hofstra university with a bachelor of science degree in communicationsread full background corporate headquarters  east main streetstamford connecticut united statesphone fax  board members memberships presentindependent directorworld wrestling entertainment inc education bs hofstra university other affiliations altice usa increntrak corporationhofstra universityrazorsight corporationcomscore incelucido media networks pvt ltdcrimson hexagon inc annual compensation there is no annual compensation data available stocks options there is no stock options data available total compensation total annual cash compensationtotal calculated compensation request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup competitor compensationnamepositioncompanycompensationrichard lewis gelfond chief executive officer and directorimax corporationmjon feltheimer chief executive officer and nonindependent directorlions gate entertainment corpmleslie moonves iichairman and chief executive officercbs corporationmmark zoradi chief executive officer and directorcinemark holdings inckshaun edward donnelly chairman ceo  cfolingerie fighting championships inckcompensation as of fiscal year  sponsored financial commentaries sponsored links browse companies a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z              request profile update only a company representative may request an update for the company profile documentation will be required to contact world wrestling entertainment inc please visit  company data is provided by sp global market intelligence please use this form to report any data issues information missing  please enter your information in the following fields company name your name your email address your phone n